ial data which can be\narbitrarily close to any shear or radial flow in $L^1$ of vorticity but do not\nweakly converge to them in the long time limit.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 7 Apr 2022 17:04:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-09"}
