cenario,\nat a later and the present stage of the cosmological evolution, where d is\nmacroscopically large, the probability to violate these conservation laws on a\nsingle DW, as a function of the inter-wall distance, is exponentially\nsuppressed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 7 Apr 2022 17:38:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-04-08"}
