r evaluated the detectability and diagnostic\npotential of CMEs from the synthetic line profiles. Our investigations provide\nimportant constraints on the future design of Sun-as-a-star spectrographs for\nCME detections through EUV line asymmetries.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 7 Apr 2022 18:32:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-06-29"}
