. The collected human-model interaction dataset and system\ncode are available at \\url{https://github.com/vipulraheja/IteraTeR}. Our system\ndemonstration is available at \\url{https://youtu.be/lK08tIpEoaE}.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 7 Apr 2022 18:33:10 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 23 Sep 2022 20:21:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-09-27"}
