ative, and shared process rather than as a\nstatic, self-contained framework to facilitate adaptability without\nannihilation of values (4) consistent life-long learning to enhance AI\naccountability\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 8 Apr 2022 00:35:14 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 17 Apr 2022 00:14:23 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 6 Dec 2022 00:24:43 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Wed, 4 Jan 2023 00:38:47 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Mon, 15 May 2023 20:18:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-17"}
