 components for optical signal\nmultiplexing and demultiplexing for wavelength division multiplexing optical\ncommunication systems. Versatile spectral responses with a simple design,\ncompact device footprint, and high fabrication tolerance make this approach\nhighly promising for flexible response shaping for many applications.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 8 Apr 2022 01:38:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-04-11"}
