\in\\{2,3\\}$ and in two dimensions $d=2$, where a CFL\ncondition is required. Then, for $d=2$, we pass to the limit in the\ndiscretization parameters and show that subsequences of discrete solutions\nconverge to a global-in-time weak solution.\n  Finally, we present numerical results.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 8 Apr 2022 15:55:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-04-11"}
