d. The different analyzed networks were in agreement with previously\npublished studies in the neonate. NeoRS is coded in Matlab, it is open-source\nand available on https://github.com/venguix/NeoRS. NeoRS allows robust image\nprocessing of the neonatal rsfMRI data that can be readily customized to\ndifferent datasets.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 8 Apr 2022 05:59:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-04-12"}
